11. **Fragment-based rendering** — Use `@st.fragment` (Streamlit 1.33+) for the workflow grid buttons so clicking a workflow doesn't rerun the entire page including KPI computation.

12. **Eliminate unnecessary reruns** — Several shells call `st.rerun()` after button clicks that already navigate via session state. The navigation happens on the next natural rerun; the explicit `st.rerun()` doubles the render cycle.

13. **Connection pooling** — The session TTL check (`SELECT 1` every 55 minutes) blocks the render thread. Move to an async pattern or reduce the check frequency to match the Streamlit session lifetime.

